attack.
Released the control of the Nest Stone!

This isn't an ordinary key, it's sealed with
magic. There might be some kind of mechanism.
Wow! Help has arrived! I'm saved!

My comrades have already been taken care of. Thank
you as always!

Well then, I'll just express my gratitude for
helping me! Take care of my comrades, okay?
I'm glad it seems like everyone is safe.

I'm so happy! Thank you! Since you've come all
this way, I'll support you with all my might!
I'm saved! Nice to meet you.
That's good. Nice to meet you.
A new loli-mon has joined the party!

Do you feel the symbol of repulsive power through
\C[2] rendering... Will you fight?

They were a tough opponent... It seems there are
still things like this scattered around...
Well then, let's return to Along with this jewel.
